Text: Hello! It’s Jackie from ruff life I went to go get your number to say the card wouldn’t work and saw that there is a card on file, the girls looked at the other Lucy not yours. It registered after because I saw their note. I was able to run Melissa’s card. Sorry for the confusion and have a great weekend!!
Good morning! I’m going to keep a closer eye on Lucy but I think she might have a UTI. She looked like she was straining to pee and only peed a tiny bit twice.
Hmm okay please let me know. She just took about 4 solid pees on the walk and 1 poop and I sensed she may have another one but had to drop off. I'll stay close by enough to come back if need be
Ok I’ll keep you updated if she goes again
Hey she did pee a tiny bit again but she’s acting normal. It’s up to you if you want to take her home or let her stay.
Ok I'll opt to keep her there and I'll stay more local than planned just in case
Thank you for watching out for her
Hi Jackie, just seeing if Lucy is A-okay
She’s been fine! A little more calm but the group is kinda calm as well so I can’t tell if it’s because of the dogs or if it’s bothering her!
